&lt;p&gt;Possible fixes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. Have serverManager handle &quot;server online&quot; event similar to how RegionServerTracker.java calls servermanager.expireServer in the case server goes down.&lt;br/&gt;
2. Make timeoutMonitor handle the situation better. This is a special situation in the cluster. 30 minutes timeout can be skipped.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
