                            <comment id="13177576" author="mingma" created="Fri, 30 Dec 2011 07:31:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are two ways to address the issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. One way is to have special handling for &quot;&lt;del&gt;ROOT&lt;/del&gt;&quot; and &quot;.META.&quot; tables.&lt;br/&gt;
2. Another way is to handle &quot;all RSs just come back online while master is up all the time&quot; scenario for all the regions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch uses the second approach.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
